    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The faculty is very interactive so the communication is good.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The events and fests held at college are quite famous.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They have contacts with celebrities because of which i am able to meet most of the celebrities",
          "name": "Chirag lodha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The facilities provided for studies are also top notch as we have library access and also air conditionerd class rooms",
          "name": "Chirag lodha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "College events ,programs and many activities",
          "name": "Ashish Bhandari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Very good teaching staff and very helpfull.",
          "name": "Ashish Bhandari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I am socialize to people's and have made a lot friends",
          "name": "Anand Kumar Pandey Pandey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college festival happening here is massive and provides a lot of exposure to the students in the committee",
          "name": "Rayyan Khot",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The schedule is just too hectic as they want students to participate in each and everything",
          "name": "Chirag lodha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They should not charge money for the passes of the college fest from the students",
          "name": "Chirag lodha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I have studied 1.5 years in online class that was a bad experience for me during covid days as I like offline classes",
          "name": "Anand Kumar Pandey Pandey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The examination results are always unexpected. Correction of papers and result declaration is unsatisfactory as marks are not given properly.",
          "name": "RUDRA KHAMBE",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The extra facilities provided in college seems to be just for name sake because there is very limited time to access the facilities.",
          "name": "RUDRA KHAMBE",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Student support: while there are support system in place, but some students feel that career counselling could be more robust",
